ing%20that%20the%20current%20owner%20only%20decided%20to%20sell%20it%20for%20%242%2C295%2C000%20due%20to%20the%20sheer%20amount%20of%20work%20it%20takes%20to%20maintain%20a%20working%20farm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20land%20is%20deeply%2C%20deeply%20meaningful%20to%20her%2C%26quot%3B%20Haley%20added.%20%26quot%3BBut%20now%2C%20she's%20in%20the%20later%20part%20of%20her%20life%2C%20and%20they're%20looking%20to%20kind%20of%20downsize.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAccording%20to%20Haley%2C%20Z%20Farm%20is%20not%20just%20any%20run-of-the-mill%20organic%20farm.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20swimming%20pond.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6542b8a4b788914e554e19b2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20swimming%20pond.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Houlihan%20Lawrence%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20land%2C%20which%20the%20current%20owner%20has%20leased%20to%20a%20farm%20company%20that%20raises%20sheep%20and%20cultivates%20vegetables%20and%20flowers%2C%20goes%20beyond%20what%20is%20expected%20of%20a%20standard%20organic%20farm%2C%20Haley%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20actually%20one%20step%20beyond%20organic.%20It's%20called%20biodynamic%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20different%20type%20of%20agriculture%20that%20takes%20it%20a%20little%20more%20in-depth%20than%20organic%20farming%2C%20so%20there's%20a%20lot%20of%20certifications%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20standards%20that%20the%20land%20and%20the%20practices%20have%20to%20meet.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBy%20continuing%20to%20lease%20the%20farmland%2C%20a%20new%20owner%20won't%20have%20to%20pay%20any%20property%20tax%2C%20Haley%20said.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20biodynamic%20farm.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6542bae3b788914e554e1ea0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20biodynamic%20farm.%3Cp%3EAnthony%20D%E2%80%99Argenzio%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20benefits%20of%20buying%20Z%20Farm%20is%20that%20a%20new%20owner%20won't%20have%20to%20pay%20any%20property%20tax.%20According%20to%20Haley%2C%20the%20onus%20of%20paying%20those%20fees%20is%20currently%20on%20the%20farm%20company%20leasing%20the%20land%20to%20raise%20livestock%20and%20grow%20vegetables.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20pay%20the%20owner%2C%20and%20then%20they%20also%20pay%20the%20taxes%20on%20the%20land%2C%26quot%3B%20Haley%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20farm%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20kind%20of%20a%20win-win%20because%20the%20farm%20company%20gets%20to%20use%20the%20land%2C%20and%20the%20owner's%20getting%20someone%20to%20manage%20it%20and%20take%20care%20of%20the%20land%2C%20and%20they're%20also%20getting%20their%20taxes%20paid%20for%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAnother%20draw%20of%20Z%20Farm%20is%20that%20a%20new%20owner%20would%20get%20to%20experience%20the%20custom-built%2C%20720-square-foot%20yurt%2C%20which%20the%20current%20owner%20rents%20out%20on%20Airbnb.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20yurt%20comes%20with%20several%20outdoor%20lounging%20and%20eating%20areas.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6542b94cb788914e554e1ab9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20yurt%20comes%20with%20several%20outdoor%20lounging%20and%20eating%20areas.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Houlihan%20Lawrence%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20the%20current%20owner%20bought%20the%20land%2C%20she%20began%20hiring%20seasonal%20farm%20workers%20who%20needed%20a%20place%20to%20stay.%20While%20building%20them%20housing%2C%20she%20decided%20to%20go%20a%20step%20further%20by%20creating%20a%20luxury%2C%20custom-built%20yurt.%3C%2Fp%3E%