long%20regarded%20as%20governing%20our%20conduct.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fembed.documentcloud.org%2Fdocuments%2F24164585-code-of-conduct-for-justices%2F%3Fembed%3D1%26responsive%3D1%26title%3D1%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22700%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Code%20of%20Conduct%20for%20Justices%20(Hosted%20by%20DocumentCloud)%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22905%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20code%20further%20lays%20out%20a%20set%20of%20criteria%20in%20which%20they%20should%20remove%20themselves%20from%20a%20case%20which%20includes%20having%20financial%20interests%20or%20any%20time%20%26quot%3Bwhere%20an%20unbiased%20and%20reasonable%20person%20who%20is%20aware%20of%20all%20relevant%20circumstances%20would%20doubt%20that%20the%20Justice%20could%20fairly%20discharge%20his%20or%20her%20duties.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20establishes%20that%20justices%20are%20allowed%20to%20attend%20fundraising%20events%2C%20but%20only%20if%20they're%20not%20on%20the%20billing%20nor%20are%20knowingly%20the%20guest%20of%20honor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStrikingly%20missing%20anywhere%20in%20its%2015%20pages%20is%20any%20form%20of%20an%20enforcement%20mechanism.%20If%20any%20single%20justice%20is%20found%20to%20have%20violated%20the%20new%20contract%2C%20there%20doesn't%20appear%20to%20be%20any%20apparent%20consequences%20other%20than%20whatever%20form%20of%20discipline%20the%20chief%20justice%20hands%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20also%20nothing%20in%20the%20code%20of%20conduct%20that%20forbids%20a%20justice%20from%20leaking%20a%20draft%20of%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20decision%20before%20it%20becomes%20official%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fleaked-draft-opinion-appears-scotus-could-overturn-roe-v-wade-2022-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eas%20is%20what%20happened%3C%2Fa%3