s.%20It%20employs%20over%2010%2C000%20permanent%20and%20temporary%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Journal's%20report%20details%20instances%20where%20a%20supervisor%20invited%20staff%20to%20a%20strip%20club%20and%20male%20workers%20sent%20their%20female%20colleagues%20unsolicited%20nude%20pictures.%20The%20men%20who%20engaged%20in%20the%20activities%20did%20not%20lose%20their%20jobs%2C%20according%20to%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20FDIC%20spokesperson%20told%20Insider%20the%20organization%20plans%20to%20conduct%20periodic%20reviews%20of%20its%20policies%20and%20programs%20around%20harassment%20and%20discrimination%20and%20it%20continually%20seeks%20feedback%20from%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHarassment%20in%20any%20form%20is%20contrary%20to%20the%20FDIC's%20values%20and%20our%20deep%20commitment%20to%20fostering%20a%20diverse%20and%20inclusive%20workplace%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20various%20training%2C%20reporting%2C%20and%20oversight%20programs%20that%20endeavor%20to%20create%20a%20safe%20and%20equitable%20environment%20where%20all%20employees%20can%20feel%20valued%20and%20respected.%20When%20we%20identify%20misconduct%2C%20we%20investigate%20and%20take%20appropriate%20action.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20the%20organization's%20inspector%20general%20criticized%20the%20FDIC's%20investigations%20into%20sexual%20harassment%2C%20calling%20them%20%26quot%3Bdecentralized%2C%20untimely%2C%20incomplete%2C%20and%20inaccurate%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Journal%20reported.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20the%20agency%20reportedly%20made%20changes%20to%20its%20policies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20FDIC%20spokesperson%20told%20the%20Journal%20that%20instances%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20have%20not%20been%20reported%20at%20the%20agency%20since%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20supervisors%20told%20the%20Journal%20they'd%20either%20visited%20strips%20clubs%20with%20their%20colleagues%20after%20work%20or%20invited%20staff%20to%20a%20strip%20club.%20One%20supervisor%2C%20Trevor%20McIntosh%2C%20said%20the%20organization%20had%20not%20told%20him%20that%20visiting%20the%20strip%20clubs%20was%20a%20problem%20and%20%26quot%3Bhe%20didn't%20know%20why%20it%20would%20have%20been%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Journal%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20FDIC%20is%20headquartered%20in%20Washington%20D.C.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655253a636d588dc55cf55e8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20FDIC%20is%20headquartered%20in%20Washington%20D.C.%3Cp%3EAnadolu%20Agency%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202015%2C%20McIntosh%20addressed%20concerns%20from%20management%20regarding%20complaints%20about%20his%20leadership%20%E2%80%94%20including%20some%20comments%20he'd%20allegedly%20made%20about%20a%20worker's%20sex%20life%20%E2%80%94%20by%20writing%20a%20memo%20detailing%20how%20he%20planned%20to%20work%20on%20his%20communication%20skills.%20Seven%20years%20later%2C%20he%20moved%20to%20a%20non-managerial%20position%20within%20the%20FDIC%2C%20the%20Journal%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESimilarly%20in%202013%2C%20another%20supervisor%2C%20Hien%20Nguyen%2C%20reportedly%20invited%20male%20colleagues%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bsex%20cafe%26quot%3B%20that%20he%20told%20the%20Journal%20was%20%26quot%3Bmore%20of%20a%20club%2Fstrip%20joint.%26quot%3B%20The%20FDIC%20demoted%20Nguyen%20after%20multiple%20workers%20told%20management%20that%20the%20supervisor%20had%20allegedly%20made%20homophobic%20and%20harassing%20comments%20to%20staff.%20Nguyen%20has%20since%20gone%20on%20to%20serve%20in%20a%20management%20position%20at%20another%20regulator%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Journal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20my%20error%20and%20lack%20of%20judgment%2C%26quot%3B%20Nguyen%20told%20the%20Journal.%20%26quot%3BI%20moved%20on%2C%20and%20I've%20learned%20from%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcInto