%20The%20monthly%20charges%20for%20four-wheelers%20are%20fixed%20at%20Rs%202%2C000%20and%20Rs%201%2C000%20for%20two-wheelers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20charges%20Rs%2010%20for%20up%20to%20four%20hours%20for%20four-wheelers%20and%20Rs%205%20for%20up%20to%20four%20hours%20for%20two-wheelers%20at%20its%20multilevel%20parking%20sites.%20The%20same%20rates%20apply%20at%20Palika%20underground%20parking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699898220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2015-02%2Fair-pollution-delhi_650x400_71423148405.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famid-rising-pollution-parking-fees-of-private-vehicles-doubled-in-delhi-4571723%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amid%20high%20pollution%20levels%20in%20the%20national%20capital%2C%20the%20New%20Delhi%20Municipal%20Council%20(NDMC)%20has%20doubled%20the%20charges%20for%20parking%20sites%20managed%20by%20it%20to%20discourage%20people%20from%20using%20private%20vehicles.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famid-rising-pollution-parking-fees-of-private-vehicles-doubled-in-delhi-4571723%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famid-rising-pollution-parking-fees-of-private-vehicles-doubled-in-delhi-4571723%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famid-rising-pollution-parking-fees-of-private-vehicles-doubled-in-delhi-4571723%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22CBI%20Asks%20Lt%20Governor%20For%20Permission%20To%20File%20FIR%20Against%20Jailed%20AAP%20Leader%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20has%20sought%20permission%20from%20the%20government%20to%20file%20a%20first%20information%20report%20(FIR)%20against%20former%20Delhi%20minister%20Satyendar%20Jain%2C%20who%20is%20in%20jail%2C%20and%20former%20Director%20General%20of%20Prisons%20Sandeep%20Goel%20for%20alleged%20extortion%20of%20crores%20of%20rupees%20from%20high-profile%20prisoners%2C%20including%20conman%20Sukesh%20Chandrashekhar%2C%20in%20return%20for%20a%20comfortable%20life%20in%20jail%2C%20sources%20said%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20request%20seeking%20sanction%20against%20Mr%20Jain%20and%20jail%20officer%20Raj%20Kumar%20was%20sent%20to%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20Vinai%20Kumar%20Saxena%2C%20while%20the%20request%20for%20permission%20to%20move%20against%20Mr%20Goel%20and%20retired%20Indian%20Administrative%20Service%20officer%20Mukesh%20Prasad%20has%20been%20sent%20to%20the%20Home%20Ministry%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20called%20the%20CBI's%20move%20%26quot%3Bnothing%20but%20mockery%20of%20law%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BAAP%20categorically%20denies%20any%20association%2C%20communication%20let%20alone%20any%20money%20transaction%20between%20Mr%20Jain%20and%20Sukesh%20Chandrasekhar%20or%20any%20of%20his%20associates%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20party%20led%20by%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20CBI%20sought%20the%20LG's%20permission%20for%20conducting%20inquiry%20against%20Satyendar%20Jain%20and%20others%20based%20only%20and%20only%20on%20the%20statement%20of%20Sukesh%20Chandrasekhar%2C%20the%20biggest%20thug%20and%20conman%20of%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20AAP%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Goel%2C%20a%201989-batch%20Indian%20Police%20Service%20(IPS)%20officer%2C%20was%20suspended%20by%20the%20Home%20Ministry%20last%20year%20after%20allegations%20of%20extortion%20were%20made%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%20has%20alleged%20it%20has%20%26quot%3Bsource%20information%26quot%3B%20that%20Mr%20Jain%2C%20Mr%20Goel%2C%20Mr%20Pra