ipper%20Rohit%20Sharma%20after%20yet%20another%20clinical%20performance%20that%20took%20Indian%20team's%20victory%20count%20to%20nine%20on%20the%20bounce.%20India%20ended%20their%20World%20Cup%20league%20stage%20beating%20the%20Netherlands%20by%20160%20runs%20here%20on%20Sunday%2C%20and%20skipper%20Rohit%20described%20their%20campaign%20so%20far%20as%20a%20clinical%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20enjoy%20each%20other's%20company.%20We%20wanted%20to%20play%20with%20enjoyment%20on%20the%20field.%20We%20try%20to%20keep%20the%20atmosphere%20outside%20lively.%20The%20results%20do%20matter%20to%20keep%20the%20dressing%20room%20lively.%20We%20are%20playing%20in%20India%2C%20there%20will%20be%20expectation.%20We%20wanted%20to%20do%20the%20job%20at%20hand.%20It's%20one%20thing%20to%20talk%20about%20it%20but%20for%20everyone%20to%20buy%20into%20it%20is%20very%20important%2C%26quot%3B%20skipper%20said%20after%20the%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERohit's%20men%20topped%20the%20league%20standings%20with%2018%20points%20and%20face%20fourth-placed%20side%20New%20Zealand%20on%20November%2015%20in%20Mumbai%20in%20the%20first%20semi-final.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVery%20pleased%20at%20how%20we've%20played%20in%20these%20nine%20games.%20Very%20clinical%20from%20game%20one%20to%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20aspect%20of%20India's%20campaign%20has%20been%20a%20total%20team%20performance%20where%20all%20eleven%20players%20have%20done%20their%20bit%20at%20some%20point%20or%20the%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDifferent%20individuals%20have%20stepped%20up%20and%20put%20their%20hand%20up%20and%20done%20the%20job.%20Everyone%20wanted%20to%20take%20the%20responsibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20started%20the%20tournament%20four%20games%20in%20a%20row%20chasing%2C%20and%20then%20we%20had%20to%20bat%20first%20and%20the%20pacers%20did%20the%20job%20along%20with%20the%20spinners.%26quot%3B%20Rohit%20said%20his%20side%20never%20looked%20too%20far%20and%20took%20one%20game%20at%20a%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSince%20we%20started%20the%20tournament%2C%20it%20was%20all%20about%20one%20game%20at%20a%20time.%20We%20never%20wanted%20to%20look%20too%20far%20ahead.%20It%20is%20a%20long%20tournament%2C%2011%20games%20in%20all%20if%20we%20go%20all%20the%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20important%20to%20break%20it%20down%20and%20focus%20on%20it.%20We%20focused%20on%20one%20game.%20We%20are%20playing%20in%20different%20venues%20and%20play%20accordingly%20and%20that's%20what%20we%20did.%20Playing%20in%20different%20venues%2C%20it%20was%20a%20challenge.%20We%20adapted%20really%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20camaraderie%20shown%20among%20the%20hosts%20players%20on%20the%20field%2C%20he%20said%2C%20Rohit%20used%20himself%2C%20Virat%20Kohli%2C%20Suryakumar%20Yadav%20and%20Shubman%20Gill%20as%20bowlers%20against%20the%20Dutch.%20He%20and%20Kohli%20even%20took%20a%20wicket%20apiece.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20it%20was%20done%20according%20to%20a%20plan%2C%20Rohit%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20something%20that%20is%20always%20in%20our%20mind.%20We%20want%20to%20create%20those%20options%20in%20the%20team%2C%20today%20we%20had%20nine%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20was%20the%20game%20we%20could%20have%20tried%20certain%20things.%20The%20seamers%20bowling%20those%20wide%20yorkers%20which%20was%20not%20needed%20but%20they%20did.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EShreyas%20Iyer%20was%20determined%20not%20to%20throw%20away%20wicket%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPlayer%20of%20the%20match%20Shreyas%20Iyer%2C%20who%20hit%20128%20not%20out%20off%2094%20balls%2C%20said%20he%20was%20determined%20not%20to%20throw%20away%20his%20wicket%20this%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20kind%20of%20had%20a%20deja%20vu.%20This%20had%20happened%20against%20Australia%20as%20well%2C%20and%20I%20threw%20my%20wicket%20and%20I%20came%2C%20but%20this%20time%20I%20wanted%20to%20come%20not%20out.%20I%20wanted%20to%20capitalise%20on%20the%20start.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWanted%20to%20pills%20I%20took%20for%20the%20cramps%20to%20kick%20in.%20Today%20it%20came%20and%20I%20am%20very%20happy.%20The%20scores%20I%20got%20in%20the%20last%20few%20days%20helped%20me.%26quot%3B%20He%20said%20the%20wicket%20was%20playing%20tacky%2C%20a%20bit%20two%20paced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20straight%20six%20he%20had%20hit%20during%20his%20magnificent%20innings%2C%20Iyer%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20worked%20a%20lot%20of%20those%20shots%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20nets.%20I%20was%20trying%20to%20hit%20straight%2C%20and%20keep%20my%20head%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGet%20into%20a%20good%20position%2C%20and%20after%20that%2C%20it%20is%20a%20follow%20through%20of%20the%20bat%20that%20ends%20behind%20my%20shoulder.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia%20showed%20pure%20class%20in%20batting%3A%20Edwards%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENetherlands%20captain%20Scott%20Edwards%20conceded%20that%20the%20Indians%20%26quot%3Bshowed%20pure%20class%20with%20the%20bat%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20(India)%20soaked%20up%20the%20pressure.%20When%20you%20are%20three%20down%20with%20ten%20overs%20left%2C%20you%20are%20going%20to%20score%20some%20runs.%20We%20are%20a%20very%20young%20side.%20Lots%20of%20young%20sides%20in%20the%20setup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20are%20as%20good%20a%20side%20going%20around.%20We%20will%20have%20to%20be%20a%20lot%20better%20going%20into%20theT20%20World%20Cup%20next%20year.%20Playing%20to%20learn%20with%20that.%26quot%3B%20Asked%20about%20the%20future%20of%20the%20team%20after%20the%20World%20Cup%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20a%20tricky%20one%20at%20the%20moment%20where%20we%20want%20to%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20pretty%20confident%20with%20the%20style%20we%20play.%20The%2