%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FIsrael%2Fstatus%2F1723664047692763459%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%2012%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fav%2Fworld-67396773%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBBC%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Sunday%2C%20Israeli%20President%20Isaac%20Herzog%20discussed%20the%20same%20and%20said%20that%20the%20book%20showed%20signs%20of%20personal%20use.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20Adolf%20Hitler's%20book%2C%20'Mein%20Kampf%2C'%20translated%20into%20Arabic.%20This%20is%20the%20book%20that%20led%20to%20the%20Holocaust%20and%20the%20book%20that%20led%20to%20World%20War%20II%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20outlet.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20terrorist%20wrote%20notes%2C%20marked%20the%20sections%20and%20studied%20again%20and%20again%2C%20Adolf%20Hitler's%20ideology%20to%20hate%20the%20Jews%2C%20to%20kill%20the%20Jews%2C%20to%20burn%20and%20slaughter%20Jews%20wherever%20they%20are.%20This%20is%20the%20real%20war%20we%20are%20facing%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Israeli%20President%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20his%20office%20also%20issued%20a%20statement%20about%20the%20discovery%20of%20the%20book.%20%26quot%3BAfter%20the%20massacre%20and%20atrocities%20committed%20by%20Hamas%20terrorists%20on%20October%207%20-%20the%20day%20on%20which%20the%20largest%20number%20of%20Jews%20were%20murdered%20since%20the%20Holocaust%20-%20this%20is%20another%20revelation%20that%20testifies%20to%20the%20sources%20of%20inspiration%20of%20the%20terrorist%20organization%20Hamas%2C%20and%20proves%20once%20again%20that%20all%20its%20actions%20have%20the%20same%20goal%20as%20the%20Nazis%20-%20the%20destruction%20of%20Jews%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Herzog's%20office%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Fox%20News%2C%20Mein%20Kampf%20means%20'My%20Struggle'%20in%20English%20and%20promotes%20the%20key%20components%20of%20Nazism.%20%C2%A0Published%20in%201925%2C%20the%20387-pa