it%20over%20how%20can%20we%20use%20Virat.%20Obviously%2C%20with%20the%20new%20ball%2C%20he%20gets%20it%20to%20swing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20challenge%20with%20Virat%20was%20the%20middle%20phase%2C%20which%20he%20did%20in%20this%20match.%20We%20want%20to%20push%20him%20further.%20He%20does%20have%20those%20in-dipping%20sharp%20yorkers%20to%20the%20right%20handers%2C%26quot%3B%20Mhambrey%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuryakumar%20and%20Gill%20have%20not%20bowled%20much%20in%20the%20past%20but%20Mhambrey%20said%20that%20both%20of%20them%20are%20'work%20in%20progress'%20and%20both%20the%20team%20management%20as%20well%20as%20the%20skipper%20want%20to%20train%20them%20in%20this%20department.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShubman%20Gill%20and%20Suryakumar%20Yadav%20are%20a%20work%20in%20progress.%20I%20thought%20at%20a%20certain%20stage%2C%20with%20the%20flight%20that%20Surya%20was%20giving%2C%20I%20was%20afraid%20for%20the%20spider%20cam.%20Luckily%2C%20he%20did%20not%20go%20any%20higher.%20But%20I%20think%20Shubman%20is%20getting%20there%2C%20but%20definitely%20a%20work%20in%20progress%20with%20both%20these%20guys.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'll%20tell%20you%20honestly%2C%20it's%20been%20two%20years%20since%20I've%20been%20after%20Rohit%20about%20this%2C%20to%20get%20Surya%20bowling%20in%20the%20match%20and%20finally%20even%20the%20captain%20rolled%20his%20arm%20over.%20I%20could%20see%20the%20glimpse%20of%20him%2C%20Virat%2C%20Shubman%2C%20all%20of%20them%20bowling%20in%20the%20nets%2C%20finally%20happy%20to%20see%20that%20in%20a%20match%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699890180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fkj7du7no_s_625x300_13_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fcricket-world-cup-2023-on-suryakumar-yadavs-bowling-india-coachs-hilarious-spider-cam-statement-4570475%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Ind