ara%20and%20Dandalgaon%20in%20Uttarkashi%2C%20is%20part%20of%20the%20Chardham%20project.%20Once%20finished%2C%20it%20is%20expected%20to%20cut%20down%20the%20distance%20by%2026%20km.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPreliminary%20information%20is%20that%20a%20landslide%20has%20caused%20part%20of%20the%20tunnel%20to%20collapse.%20Chief%20Minister%20Pushkar%20Singh%20Dhami%20has%20said%20that%20the%20soil%20in%20the%20area%20is%20loose%20and%20that%20is%20why%20debris%20keeps%20falling%2C%20which%20is%20why%20the%20rescue%20operation%20is%20also%20taking%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bundela%20agreed.%20%26quot%3BThe%20soil%20is%20very%20loose%E2%80%A6%20so%20when%20the%20machines%20start%20making%20the%20way%2C%20they%20have%20to%20be%20very%20careful%20(not%20to%20harm%20people%20or%20cause%20additional%20damage)%E2%80%A6%C2%A0%20the%20work%20has%20to%20be%20very%20meticulous%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20had%20initially%20been%20able%20to%20cut%20through%2030%20meters%20of%20rocks%20but%20some%20soil%20fell%20again%20so%20they%20have%20been%20able%20to%20clear%2014%20meters.%20Asked%20how%20much%20further%20they%20have%20to%20go%2C%20he%20said%20it%20is%20difficult%20to%20predict%20but%20an%20estimate%20by%20NHIDCR%20(National%20Highways%20and%20Infrastructure%20Development)%20is%20that%20rocks%20have%20fallen%20in%20an%20area%20that%20is%2040%20meters%20in%20length.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVideos%20from%20the%20spot%20showed%20huge%20piles%20of%20concrete%20blocking%20the%20tunnel%2C%20twisted%20metal%20bars%20from%20its%20broken%20roof%20buried%20in%20rubble%20creating%20more%20obstacles%20for%20rescue%20workers.%20Around%20160%20rescue%20workers%20are%20trying%20to%20reach%20the%20trapped%20labourers%20with%20drilling%20equipment%20and%20excavators.%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20police%20said%20portion%20of%20the%20tunnel%20collapsed%20around%204%20am%20on%20Sunday.%20Alarm%20was%20raised%20immediately%20and%20rescue%20workers%20rushed%20to%20the%20spot.%20The%20Chief%20Minister%20has%20also%20visited%20the%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trapped%20workers%20are%20mostly%20migrants%20from%20Bihar%2C%20Jharkhand%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20West%20Bengal%2C%20Odisha%2C%20Uttarakhand%20and%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20officials%20have%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699887840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fljcep05k_uttarakhand-tunnel-collapse_625x300_12_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Futtarakhand-tunnel-collapse-rescue-efforts-at-uttarakhand-tunnel-go-slow-senior-official-explains-why-4571357%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Efforts%20are%20on%20to%20rescue%20the%2040%20workers%20inside%20an%20under-construction%20tunnel%20in%20Uttarakhand%20that%20collapsed%20early%20on%20Sunday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Futtarakhand-tunnel-collapse-rescue-efforts-at-uttarakhand-tunnel-go-slow-senior-official-explains-why-4571357%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Futtarakhand-tunnel-collapse-rescue-efforts-at-uttarakhand-tunnel-go-slow-senior-official-explains-why-4571357%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Futtarakhand-tunnel-collapse-rescue-efforts-at-uttarakhand-tunnel-go-slow-senior-official-explains-why-4571357%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rohit%20Becomes%201st%20Indian%20Captain%20To%20Register%20This%20Massive%20World%20Cup%20Record%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia%20skipper%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F857-rohit-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E%20continues%20his%20red-form%20in%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023.%20In%20the%20nine%20matches%20played%20in%20the%20league%20stage%20of%20the%20tournament%2C%20the%20