20or%20adjusting%20the%20shape%20of%20a%20structure%20approximately%20265%20meters%20inside%20the%20tunnel.%20A%20portion%20of%20the%20tunnel%2C%20almost%2050%20to%2055%20metres%20away%20from%20them%2C%20collapsed%2C%20trapping%20them%20inside.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20rescue%20work%20started%20immediately%20after%20the%20incident%20was%20reported.%20One%20of%20the%20priorities%20for%20the%20rescue%20teams%20was%20to%20ensure%20the%20supply%20of%20food%20and%20oxygen%20to%20the%20trapped%20workers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EEssentials%20like%20medicines%2C%20food%2C%20water%2C%20electricity%20and%20oxygen%20were%20supplied%20in%20the%20trapped%20portion%20through%20pipes.%20The%20rescue%20teams%20successfully%20established%20communication%20with%20the%20workers%20with%20Walkie-Talkies.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAccording%20to%20preliminary%20reports%2C%20a%20landslide%20in%20the%20region%20triggered%20a%20collapse.%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Uttarakhand%20Pushkar%20Singh%20Dhami%20said%20loose%20soil%20is%20causing%20the%20debris%20to%20fall%2C%20because%20of%20which%20there's%20a%20delay%20in%20rescue%20operations.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20loose%20debris%2C%20which%20is%20delaying%20the%20rescue%20operations%2C%20is%20being%20stabilised%20and%20excavation%20with%20shotcreting%20for%2040%20meters%20of%20the%20collapsed%20tunnel%20has%20started.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EShotcreting%20is%20a%20term%20for%20spraying%20concrete%20at%20high%20velocity%20over%20a%20structure.%20The%20rescue%20teams%20have%20taken%20two%20important%20steps%20to%20evacuate%20the%20workers.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELoose%20dirt%20is%20being%20removed%20along%20with%20shotcreting-21%20meters%20of%20debris.%20A%20minor%20fall%20of%20the%20debris%20has%20reduced%20the%20excavation%20to%2014%20metres.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20rescue%20teams%20are%20planning%20to%20push%20a%20pipe%20with%20a%20900%20mm%20diameter%20using%20a%20hydraulic%20jack%20by%20boring%20a%20hole%20into%20the%20heap%20of%20debris%20to%20evacuate%20the%20trapped%20workers.%20All%20the%20material%20and%20machinery%20needed%20for%20the%20daring%20operation%20is%20being%20mobilised.%20Experts%20from%20the%20irrigation%20department%20have%20also%20joined%20the%20operation.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%204.5%20km-long%20tunnel%20connects%20Silkyara%20to%20the%20Gangotri-Yamnotri%20axis%20and%20is%20a%20part%20of%20the%20Centre's%20Chardham%20Mahamarg%20Pariyojana.%20The%20workers%20are%20stuck%20in%20a%20400-metre%20buffer%20zone%20in%20the%20tunnel%20and%20are%20reportedly%20safe.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699886040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F69ajtms_tunnel_625x300_13_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F40-workers-trapped-in-uttarakhand-tunnel-may-take-2-more-days-to-rescue-4571266%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Around%2040%20workers%20are%20trapped%20inside%20an%20under-construction%20tunnel%20for%20over%2024%20hours%20in%20Uttarakhand's%20Uttarkashi.%20Secretary%20Disaster%20Management%20Ranjit%20Kumar%20Sinha%20who%20visited%20the%20tunnel%20said%20it%20may%20take%20two%20more%20days%20to%20rescue%20the%20trapped%20workers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F40-workers-trapped-in-uttarakhand-tunnel-may-take-2-more-days-to-rescue-4571266%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F40-workers-trapped-in-uttarakhand-tunnel-may-take-2-more-days-to-rescue-4571266%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F40-workers-trapped-in-uttarakhand-tunnel-may-take-2-more-days-to-rescue-4571266%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pentagon%20UFO%20Chief%20Resigns%20After%20Warning%20About%20Aliens%2C%20Rival%20Tech%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20chief%20of%20the%20Pentagon's%20UFO%20investigation%20division%20will%20step%20down%20in%20December%2C%20the%20Department%20of%20Defence%20said.%20Sean%20Kirkpatrick%2C%20Director%20of%20the%20All-Domain%20Anomaly%20Resolution%20Office%20(AARO)%2C%20announced%20his%20retirement%20after%20a%2027-year%20career%20in%20the%20department%20and%20the%20United%20States%20Intelligence%20Community.%20He%20announced%20his%20plans%20after%20leading%20the%20department%20for%2018%20months.%20He%20stated%20that%20sightings%20of%20objects%20flying%20in%20the%20sky%20over%20the%20US%20are%20either%20aliens%20or%20technology%20of%20rival%20nations.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20ready%20to%20move%20on.%20I%20have%20accomplished%20everything%20I%20said%20I%20was%20going%20to%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kirkpatrick%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.com%2Fnews%2F2023%2F11%2F07%2Fpentagon-ufo-boss-00125883%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EPolitico%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20said%20that%20he%20still%20wants%20to%20finish%20%26quot%3Bwrapping%20up%20the%20first%20volume%20of%20a%20historical%20review%20of%20the%20unidentified%20anomalous%20phenomena%20issue%26quot%3B%2C%20before%20leaving%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kirkpatrick%20warned%20of%20the%20presence%20of%20UFOs%20after%20studying%20more%20than%20800%20instances%20during%20his%20tenure%20as%20director%2C%20and%20while%20there%20has%20yet%20to%20be%20any%20firm%20evidence%20of%20aliens%2C%20he%20felt%20the%20alternative%20was%20much%20more%20frightening.%20%26quot%3BIf%20we%20don't%20prove%20it's%20aliens%2C%20then%20what%20we're%20finding%20is%20evidence%20of%20other%20people%20doing%20stuff%20in%20our%20backyard.%20And%20that's%20not%20good%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20announcement%20comes%20barely%20a%20week%20after%20Mr%20Kirkpatrick%20stated%20that%20AARO%20will%20create%20a%20reporting%20mechanism%20for%20current%20and%20former%20US%20federal%20employees%20and%20contractors%20who%20witnessed%20US%20government-related%20actions%20involving%20unidentified%20anomalous%20phenomena.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20system%20was%20established%20just%20months%20after%20former%20US%20intelligence%20official%20David%20Grusch%20testified%20before%20Congress%20that%20the%20Pentagon%20had%20recovered%20wrecked%20vehicles%20of%20unknown%20origin%20containing%20%26quot%3Bnon-human%20biologics.%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kirkpatrick%20claimed%20that%20he%20has%20frequently%20requested%20Mr%20Grusch%20for%20additional%20evidence%20to%20back%20up%20his%20assertions%20and%20has%20received%20no%20response.%20The%20Pentagon%20has%20insisted%20that%20it%20was%20unaware%20of%20any%20reverse%20engineering%20efforts%2C%20craft%20recovery%2C%20or%20discoveries%20pertaining%20to%20%26quot%3Bnon-human%20biologics.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Department%20of%20Defence%20praised%20Kirkpatrick's%20leadership%20and%20credited%20him%20for%20building%20the%20organisation's%20first%20website%20that%20was%20accessible%20to%20the%20public%2C%20increasing%20the%20AARO's%20level%20of%20transparency.%20%26quot%3BHis%20commitment%20to%20transparency%20with%20the%20United%20States%20Congress%20and%20the%20American%20public%20on%20UAP%20(Unidentified%20Aerial%20Phenomena)%20leaves%20a%20legacy%20the%20department%20will%20carry%20forward%20as%20AARO%20continues%20its%20mission.%20Our%20department%20is%20stronger%20and%20better%20prepared%20for%20future%20scientific%20and%20national%20security%20challenges%20because%20of%20Sean's%20distinguished%20service%20to%20our%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20statement%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETim%20Phillips%20will%20serve%20as%20the%20deputy%20director%20of%20AARO%20until%20the%20Pentagon%20appoints%20a%20permanent%20replacement%2C%20according%20to%20the%20statement%20from%20the%20Defence%20Department.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699885980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fq9vvku_aaro_625x300_13_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%