20State%20Department%2C%20including%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Anthony%20Blinken%2C%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20ongoing%20Israel-Hamas%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Fus-entity-list-israeli-spyware-nso-group-pegasus-trade-blacklist-malicious-cyber-activities%5C%22%3ETwo%20years%20ago%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20US%20government%20added%20Israeli%20companies%2C%20NSO%20group%20and%20Candiru%20to%20the%20Commerce%20Department%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98entity%20list%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20is%20a%20federal%20blacklist%20that%20would%20restrict%20exports%20of%20US%20technology%20to%20the%20company.%20The%20move%20was%20dictated%20by%20%E2%80%9Cevidence%20that%20these%20entities%20developed%20and%20supplied%20spyware%20to%20foreign%20governments%20that%20used%20these%20tools%20to%20maliciously%20target%20government%20officials%2C%20journalists%2C%20businesspeople%2C%20activists%2C%20academics%2C%20and%20embassy%20workers%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20been%20part%20of%20an%20international%20collaborative%20investigation%20known%20as%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fproject-pegasus-journalists-ministers-activists-phones-spying%5C%22%3EPegasus%20Project%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%2C%20that%20tracked%20the%20leaked%20database%20of%20thousands%20of%20telephone%20numbers%20that%20were%20believed%20to%20have%20been%20listed%20by%20multiple%20government%20clients%20of%20NSO%20group.%20Comprising%2017%20news%20organisations%20in%2010%20countries%2C%20the%20Pegasus%20Project%20was%20coordinated%20by%20Forbidden%20Stories%20with%20technical%20support%20of%20Amnesty%20International.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20couple%20of%20months%20after%20being%20blacklisted%2C%20NSO%20group%20hired%20a%20law%20firm%2C%20Los%20Angeles-based%20Paul%20Hastings%20LLP%2C%20to%20conduct%20an%20active%20lobbying%20effort%20to%20get%20out%20of%20the%20entity%20list%20in%20January%202022.%20This%20was%20initially%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fnso-group-pegasus-lobbying-us-trade-blacklist%5C%22%3Ereported%20by%20%3Cem%3EProPublica%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20November%207%2C%20partner%20at%20Paul%20Hastings%2C%20Timothy%20Dickinson%2C%20sent%20a%20letter%20and%20an%20email%20to%20request%20an%20%E2%80%9Curgent%20meeting%E2%80%9D%20to%20the%20US%20State%20Department.%20The%20documents%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fefile.fara.gov%2Fdocs%2F6743-Informational-Materials-20231107-22.pdf%5C%22%3Epublicly%20filed%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20the%20Justice%20Department%20as%20part%20of%20the%20Foreign%20Agents%20Registration%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENSO%20Group%E2%80%99s%20latest%20action%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheintercept.com%2F2023%2F11%2F10%2Fnso-group-israel-gaza-blacklist%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%20first%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Intercept%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20writing%20on%20behalf%20of%20%5Bthe%5D%20NSO%20Group%20to%20urgently%20request%20an%20opportunity%20to%20engage%20with%20Secretary%20Blinken%20and%20the%20officials%20at%20the%20State%20Department%20regarding%20the%20importance%20of%20cyber%20intelligence%20technology%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20grave%20security%20threats%20posed%20by%20the%20recent%20Hamas%20terrorist%20attacks%20in%20Israel%20and%20their%20aftermath%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Haaretz%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20earlier%20reported%20that%20NSO%20and%20other%20Israeli%20spyware%20firms%20had%20been%20working%20with%20the%20Israeli%20government%20to%20track%20down%20missing%20hostages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQuoting%20experts%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Intercept%20%3C%2Fem%3Enoted%20that%20the%20NSO%20was%20using%20the%20current%20crisis%20to%20make%20space%20for%20the%20group%20to%20return%20to%20the%20good%20books%20of%20Washington.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNSO%E2%80%99s%20participation%20in%20the%20Israeli%20government%E2%80%99s%20efforts%20to%20locate%20citizens%20in%20Gaza%20seems%20to%20be%20an%20effort%20by%20the%20company%20to%20rehabilitate%20its%20image%20in%20this%20crisis%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Adam%20Shapiro%2C%20director%20of%20advocacy%20for%20Israel-Palestine%20at%20Democracy%20for%20the%20Arab%20World%20Now%2C%20a%20group%20founded%20by%20the%20slain%20journalist%20Jamal%20Khashoggi%20to%20advocate%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheintercept.com%2F2020%2F09%2F30%2Fjamal-khashoggi-dawn-saudi%2F%5C%22%3Ehuman%20rights%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0in%20the%20Middle%20East.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20alarm%20bells%20should%20be%20ringing%20that%20NSO%20Group%20has%20been%20recruited%20in%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20war%20effort.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Pegasus%20Project%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fpegasus-hacking-jamal-khashoggi-wife%5C%22%3Ehad%20traced%20the%20use%20of%20the%20Pegasus%20spyware%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20phones%20of%20close%20kin%20of%20Khashoggi%20prior%20and%20after%20his%20killing%20inside%20the%20Saudi%20consulate%20in%20Ankara.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20letter%20to%20Blinken%2C%20Dickinson%20wrote%20that%20%E2%80%9CNSO%E2%80%99s%20technology%20is%20supporting%20the%20current%20global%20fight%20against%20terrorism%20in%20any%20and%20all%20forms.%20These%20efforts%20squarely%20align%20with%20the%20Biden-Harris%20administration%E2%80%99s%20repeated%20messages%20and%20actions%20of%20support%20for%20the%20Israeli%20government%2C%20including%20from%20a%20defense%20and%20cybersecurity%20perspective.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20the%20technology%20can%20be%20%E2%80%9Cmisused%E2%80%9D%20by%20end-users%20to%20violate%20human%20rights%2C%20but%20claimed%20that%20NSO%20had%20taken%20%E2%80%9Cconcrete%20steps%20to%20address%20potential%20downstream%20human%20rights%20impacts%20of%20its%20products%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NSO%20group%20had%20been%20in%20financial%20doldrums%20since%20it%20came%20into%20public%20spotlight%20through%20the%20Pegasus%20Project%20and%20then%20the%20blacklisting%20by%20the%20US%20Commerce%20Department.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2F24584247-0fd4-4826-bcac-f726ad17af58%3FshareType%3Dnongift%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Financial%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20reported%20in%202022%20that%20the%20value%20of%20NSO%20had%20been%20deemed%20worthless%20to%20its%20private%20equity%20backers%20and%20has%20not%20received%20any%20new%20customer%20bookings%20since%20July%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699884020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F07%2F24204013%2FIMG_4150.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fciting-the-israel-hamas-war-nso-group-sought-urgent-meeting-with-blinken%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Quoting%20experts%2C%20The%20Intercept%20noted%20that%20the%20NSO%20was%20using%20the%20current%20crisis%20to%20make%20space%20for%20the%20group%20to%20return%20to%20the%20good%20books%20of%20Washington.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fciting-the-israel-hamas-war-nso-group-sought-urgent-meeting-with-blinken%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Uganda%20attack%3A%20Man%20charged%20with%20terrorism%20over%20honeymoon%20deaths%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699883918000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F09D9%2Fproduction%2F_131712520_suplied.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-67402358%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Abdul%20Rashid%20Kyoto%20is%20accused%20of%20killing%20British%20and%20South%20African%20honeymooners%20and%20their%20Ugandan%20guide.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A31%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-67402358%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-b