i-123111300747_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fadani-used-renewable-source-to-supply-4-hrs-of-power-to-mumbai-on-diwali-123111300747_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fadani-used-renewable-source-to-supply-4-hrs-of-power-to-mumbai-on-diwali-123111300747_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Israeli%20Tanks%20Outside%20Gaza%20Hospital%2C%20Doctors%20Say%20%26quot%3BStuck%20In%20Circle%20Of%20Death%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20forces%20reached%20the%20gates%20of%20Gaza%20City's%20main%20hospital%20on%20Monday%2C%20the%20primary%20target%20in%20their%20battle%20to%20seize%20control%20of%20the%20northern%20half%20of%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20where%20medics%20said%20patients%20including%20newborn%20babies%20were%20dying%20for%20lack%20of%20fuel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGaza%20health%20ministry%20spokesperson%20Ashraf%20Al-Qidra%2C%20who%20was%20inside%20Al%20Shifa%20hospital%2C%20said%2032%20patients%20had%20died%20in%20the%20past%20three%20days%2C%20including%20three%20newborn%20babies%2C%20as%20a%20result%20of%20the%20siege%20of%20the%20hospital%20and%20the%20cut-off%20of%20its%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20least%20650%20patients%20were%20still%20inside%2C%20desperate%20to%20be%20evacuated%20to%20another%20medical%20facility%20by%20the%20Red%20Cross%20or%20some%20other%20neutral%20agency.%20Israel%20says%20the%20hospital%20sits%20atop%20tunnels%20housing%20a%20headquarters%20for%20Hamas%20fighters%2C%20who%20are%20to%20blame%20for%20its%20plight%20for%20using%20patients%20as%20shields%2C%20which%20Hamas%20denies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20tanks%20are%20in%20front%20of%20the%20hospital.%20We%20are%20under%20full%20blockade.%20It's%20a%20totally%20civilian%20area.%20Only%20hospital%20facility%2C%20hospital%20patients%2C%20doctors%20and%20other%20civilians%20staying%20in%20the%20hospital.%20Someone%20should%20stop%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20surgeon%20at%20the%20hospital%2C%20Dr%20Ahmed%20El%20Mokhallalati%2C%20said%20by%20telephone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20bombed%20the%20(water)%20tanks%2C%20they%20bombed%20the%20water%20wells%2C%20they%20bombed%20the%20oxygen%20pump%20as%20well.%20They%20bombed%20everything%20in%20the%20hospital.%20So%20we%20are%20hardly%20surviving.%20We%20tell%20everyone%2C%20the%20hospital%20is%20no%20more%20a%20safe%20place%20for%20treating%20patients.%20We%20are%20harming%20patients%20by%20keeping%20them%20here.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20also%20fresh%20concern%20that%20the%20war%20could%20spread%20beyond%20Gaza%2C%20with%20an%20upsurge%20of%20clashes%20on%20Israel's%20northern%20border%20with%20Lebanon%2C%20and%20the%20United%20States%20launching%20air%20strikes%20on%20Iran-linked%20militia%20targets%20in%20neighbouring%20Syria.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20launched%20its%20campaign%20last%20month%20to%20annihilate%20Hamas%2C%20the%20group%20which%20runs%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20after%20Hamas%20fighters%20rampaged%20through%20southern%20Israel%20killing%20civilians.%20Around%201%2C200%20people%20died%20and%20240%20were%20dragged%20to%20Gaza%20as%20hostages%20according%20to%20Israel's%20tally%2C%20in%20the%20deadliest%20day%20in%20its%2075-year%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20then%20thousands%20of%20Gazans%20have%20been%20killed%20and%20more%20than%20half%20of%20the%20population%20made%20homeless%20by%20a%20relentless%20Israeli%20military%20campaign.%20Israel%20has%20ordered%20the%20total%20evacuation%20of%20the%20northern%20half%20of%20Gaza.%20Gaza%20medical%20authorities%20say%20more%20than%2011%2C000%20people%20have%20been%20confirmed%20killed%2C%20around%2040%25%20of%20them%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20Israeli%20ground%20forces%20entered%20Gaza%20in%20late%20October%20and%20quickly%20surrounded%20Gaza%20City%2C%20fighting%20has%20been%20concentrated%20in%20a%20tightening%20circle%20around%20Al%20Shifa%2C%20the%20enclave's%20biggest%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGaza%20health%20ministry%20spokesperson%20Qidra%20said%20an%20Israel%20tank%20was%20now%20stationed%20at%20the%20hospital%20gate.%20Israeli%20snipers%20and%20drones%20were%20firing%20into%20the%20hospital%2C%20making%20it%20impossible%20for%20medics%20and%20patients%20to%20move%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20besieged%20and%20are%20inside%20a%20circle%20of%20death%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20told%20civilians%20to%20leave%20and%20medics%20to%20send%20patients%20elsewhere.%20It%20says%20it%20has%20attempted%20to%20evacuate%20babies%20from%20the%20neo-natal%20ward%20and%20left%20300%20litres%20of%20fuel%20to%20power%20emergency%20generators%20at%20the%20hospital%20entrance%2C%20but%20the%20offers%20were%20blocked%20by%20Hamas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQidra%20said%20the%20300%20litres%20would%20power%20the%20hospital%20for%20just%20half%20an%20hour%2C%20and%20Shifa%20needed%208%2C000-10%2C000%20litres%20of%20fuel%20per%20day%20delivered%20by%20the%20Red%20Cross%20or%20an%20international%20agency.%20An%20Israeli%20official%20who%20requested%20anonymity%20said%20300%20litres%20could%20last%20several%20hours%20because%20only%20the%20emergency%20room%20was%20running.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20El%20Mokhallalati%2C%20the%20surgeon%2C%20said%20premature%20babies%20that%20would%20normally%20be%20in%20individual%20incubators%20were%20being%20lined%20up%20eight%20to%20a%20bed%2C%20kept%20warm%20with%20whatever%20power%20was%20left.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20three%20died%20there%20were%2036%20alive%20in%20the%20neo-natal%20unit%2C%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20expecting%20to%20lose%20more%20of%20them%20day%20by%20day.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20second%20major%20hospital%20in%20northern%20Gaza%2C%20al-Quds%2C%20has%20also%20stopped%20functioning.%20The%20Palestinian%20Red%20Crescent%20said%20it%20was%20surrounded%20by%20heavy%20gunfire%2C%20and%20a%20convoy%20of%20Red%20Cross%20vehicles%20sent%20to%20evacuate%20patients%20and%20staff%20had%20been%20unable%20to%20reach%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EU.N.%20agencies%20observed%20a%20minute's%20silence%20on%20Monday%20for%20101%20staff%20members%20killed%20so%20far%2C%20the%20largest%20toll%20of%20humanitarian%20workers%20in%20any%20war%20since%20the%20U.N.%20was%20founded%20in%20the%20ashes%20of%20World%20War%20Two.%20The%20United%20Nations%20has%20run%20a%20huge%20operation%20for%20generations%20in%20Gaza%2C%20where%20most%20residents%20are%20refugees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPOLARISED%20WORLD%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20more%20than%20month-long%20conflict%20has%20polarised%20the%20world%2C%20with%20many%20countries%20saying%20that%20even%20the%20shocking%20brutality%20of%20the%20Hamas%20attacks%20did%20not%20justify%20an%20Israeli%20response%20that%20has%20killed%20so%20many%20civilians%20in%20a%20crowded%20territory%20under%20siege.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20says%20it%20must%20destroy%20Hamas%2C%20and%20the%20blame%20for%20harm%20to%20civilians%20falls%20on%20fighters%20who%20hide%20among%20them.%20It%20has%20rejected%20demands%20for%20a%20ceasefire%2C%20which%20it%20says%20would%20only%20prolong%20the%20suffering%20by%20giving%20Hamas%20a%20chance%20to%20regroup.%20Washington%20backs%20that%20position%20though%20it%20says%20it%20is%20nevertheless%20pressing%20its%20ally%20to%20protect%20civilians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20United%20States%20does%20not%20want%20to%20see%20firefights%20in%20hospitals%20where%20innocent%20people%2C%20patients%20receiving%20medical%20care%2C%20are%20caught%20in%20the%20crossfire%20and%20we've%20had%20active%20consultations%20with%20the%20Israeli%20Defence%20Forces%20on%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20White%20House%20National%20Security%20Adviser%20Jake%20Sullivan%20told%20CBS%20News.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20civilians%20are%20believed%20to%20remain%20in%20the%20northern%20part%20of%20Gaza%20despite%20Israel's%20order%20to%20leave.%20Israel%20has%20also%20regularly%20bombed%20the%20south.%20Health%20officials%20said%20at%20least%2014%20people%20were%20killed%20in%20two%20separate%20strikes%20in%20the%20main%20southern%20Gaza%20city%2C%20Khan%20Younis.%20At%20Nasser%20Hospital%2C%20people%20in%20private%20cars%20brought%20in%20casualties%20including%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20dead%20bodies%20under%20the%20rubble%2C%20we%20need%20ambulances%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20of%20the%20men%20cried.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20conflict%20has%20raised%20fears%20of%20a%20broader%20conflagration.%20Lebanon-based%20Hezbollah%2C%20which%20like%20Hamas%20is%20backed%20by%20Iran%2C%20has%20traded%20missile%20attacks%20with%20Israel.%20Other%20Iran-backed%20groups%20in%20Iraq%20and%20Syria%20have%20launched%20at%20least%2040%20drone%20and%20rocket%20attacks%20on%20U.S.%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20States%20carried%20out%20two%20air%20strikes%20in%20Syria%20against%20Iran-aligned%20groups%20on%20Sunday%2C%20a%20U.S.%20defense%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699880280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fhm29vmlg_gaza-al-shifa-hospital-gaza-hospital-_625x300_13_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisraeli-tanks-outside-gaza-hospital-doctors-say-stuck-in-circle-of-death-4570976%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Israeli%20forces%20reached%20the%20gates%20of%20Gaza%20City's%20main%20hospital%20on%20Monday%2C%20the%20primary%20target%20in%20their%20battle%20to%20seize%20control%20of%20the%20northern%20half%20of%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20where%20medics%20said%20patients%20including%20newborn%20babies%20were%20dying%20for%20l