C%20Suella%20Braverman%2C%20for%20persistently%20going%20off-message%20in%20her%20public%20remarks.%20Her%20latest%20incendiary%20comments%20have%20been%20to%20denounce%20huge%20pro-Palestine%20protests%20in%20London%20as%20%E2%80%98hate%20marches%E2%80%99%20and%20to%20accuse%20London%E2%80%99s%20police%20of%20political%20bias%20in%20the%20way%20they%20deal%20with%20these%20demonstrations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBraverman%20had%20become%20a%20liability.%20Her%20comments%20last%20week%20clearly%20undermined%20confidence%20in%20the%20police%20%E2%80%93%20exactly%20the%20opposite%20of%20what%20you%20would%20expect%20a%20home%20secretary%2C%20the%20minister%20in%20charge%20of%20law%20and%20order%2C%20to%20do.%20She%20accused%20London%E2%80%99s%20police%20of%20left-wing%20bias%20in%20dealing%20with%20protests%20demanding%20a%20ceasefire%20in%20Gaza%20and%20publicly%20%E2%80%93%20but%20unsuccessfully%20%E2%80%93%20urged%20the%20police%20to%20ban%20the%20most%20recent%20march%20on%20Saturday%20which%20was%20attended%20by%20half-a-million%20or%20so%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuella%20Braverman%20has%20form%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20eye-catching%20and%20deeply%20illiberal%20remarks%3A%20she%20has%20described%20the%20flow%20of%20illegal%20immigrants%20crossing%20the%20Channel%20in%20small%20boats%20as%20an%20invasion%3B%20she%20has%20championed%20the%20bizarre%20scheme%20to%20offload%20some%20of%20these%20illegal%20immigrants%20to%20Rwanda%20in%20central%20Africa%3B%20she%20recently%20said%20that%20some%20of%20the%20homeless%2C%20camping%20on%20city%20centre%20pavements%20in%20cheap%2C%20tiny%20tents%2C%20had%20made%20a%20lifestyle%20choice%2C%20suggesting%20that%E2%80%99s%20the%20way%20they%20wanted%20to%20live.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhy%20has%20Braverman%20made%20such%20a%20string%20of%20inflammatory%20comments%3F%20Well%2C%20probably%20because%20she%20really%20believes%20what%20she%E2%80%99s%20saying.%20She%20is%20on%20the%20right%20wing%20of%20the%20Conservative%20Party%2C