ings%20in%20the%20parliament.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20any%20of%20us%20is%20either%20inclined%20or%20able%20to%20investigate%20these%20amorphous%20charges%20against%20her%2C%20so%20let%E2%80%99s%20lay%20that%20aside%20for%20the%20moment.%20Of%20course%2C%20with%20the%20proof%20that%20her%20log%20in%20was%20repeatedly%20used%20from%20Dubai%20and%20that%20the%20National%20Informatics%20Centre%20(NIC)%20portal%20has%20been%20%E2%80%98compromised%E2%80%99%2C%20national%20security%20has%20entered%20the%20discussion.%20Dangerous%20potential%20leaks%20to%20foreign%20countries%20have%20been%20speculated%20on%20and%20the%20stage%20is%20set%20for%20the%20entry%20of%20the%20dastardly%20George%20Soros.%20(He%20has%2C%20actually%2C%20already%20entered%20the%20picture%20in%20veiled%20references%20to%20the%20Hindenburg%20report.)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20lies%20ahead%20is%20the%20grand%20spectacle%20of%20Moitra%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Flok-sabha-ethics-committee-recommends-expulsion-of-tmc-mp-mahua-moitra-from-lok-sabha%5C%22%3Eexpulsion%20from%20parliament%20on%20the%20very%20first%20day%20of%20the%20upcoming%20winter%20session%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20is%20reminiscent%20of%20the%20unseemly%20haste%20with%20which%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20summary%20suspension%20was%20carried%20out%20earlier%20this%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMoitra%20and%20Gandhi%2C%20by%20the%20way%2C%20are%20connected%20by%20their%20focus%20on%20questioning%20Adani.%20Neither%20of%20them%20shies%20away%20from%20foregrounding%20the%20fascism%20of%20the%20current%20dispensation%20and%20the%20unfolding%20danger%20to%20the%20Indian%20polity%20from%20this.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmahua-moitra-says-neither-quid-nor-quo-only-slander-all-questions-in-parliament-were-hers%5C%22%3EMahua%20Moitra%20Says%20neither%20%E2%80%98Quid%E2%80%99%20nor%20%E2%80%98Quo%E2%80%99%2C%20Only%20Slander%3B%20All%20Questions%20in%20Parliament%20Were%20Hers%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20I%20would%20like%20to%20focus%20on%20here%20is%20the%20use%20of%20maryada%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Eand%20garima%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Ein%20the%20discourse%20around%20Moitra.%20These%20categories%20are%20continually%20invoked%20by%20way%20of%20maintaining%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Esadan%20ki%20garima%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E(parliamentary%20decorum)%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eand%20the%20language%20Moitra%20used%20at%20the%20meeting%2C%20which%20is%20seen%20as%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Easansadya%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(unparliamentary).%20It%20is%20also%20language%20which%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20suit%20a%20woman%20or%20as%20Vinod%20Kumar%20Sonkar%2C%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20Ethics%20Committee%20said%2C%E2%80%9D..e%3Cem%3Ek%20saansad%20aur%20ek%20mahila%20saansad%20ko%20shobha%20nahin%20deti%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20interchangeable%20categories%20are%20not%20only%20summoned%20in%20terms%20of%20language%2C%20but%20also%20in%20other%20figurative%20ways.%20Moitra%E2%80%99s%20women%20counterparts%20from%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20invoke%2C%20tacitly%2C%20the%20question%20of%20women%E2%80%99s%20honour%20by%20their%20expressive%20adornment.%20The%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Emangalsutra%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Esindoor%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E(vermillion)%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Econveys%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Etheir%20own%20story%20of%20the%20difference%20between%20those%20who%20stand%20for%20conventional%20Indian%20womanhood%20and%20the%20likes%20of%20%E2%80%98women%20like%20Moitra%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20this%20context%2C%20many%20of%20us%20might%20remember%20the%20deployment%20of%20the%20late%20Sushma%20Swaraj%20as%20the%20champion%20of%20Indian%20womanhood%20against%20a%20tainted%20and%20foreign%20Sonia%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESpeech%20and%20utterance%20matter%3B%20the%20measured%20speech%20of%20these%20women%20is%20inscribed%20within%20the%20moral%20code%20of%20this%20womanhood%20and%20its%20place%20in%20the%20nation.%20It%20is%20a%20mark%20of%20their%20seriousness%20as%20defenders%20of%20the%20regime%20and%20its%20moral%20strictures.%20Their%20speech%20also%20stands%20in%20contrast%20to%20Moitra%E2%80%99s%20own%20utterances%2C%20censured%20not%20only%20for%20the%20fluency%20of%20her%20articulation%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Eof%20very%20real%20dangers%20but%20also%20for%20the%20possible%20anarchy%20that%20women%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98intemperate%E2%80%99%20speech%20signals.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0These%20women%20say%20they%20aren%E2%80%99t%20the%20slightest%20bit%20interested%20in%20Moitra%E2%80%99s%20personal%20life.%20This%20bit%20of%20disingenuousness%20would%20be%20funny%20if%20it%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20so%20disturbing%2C%20like%20everything%20else%20that%20plays%20out%20these%20days%20in%20this%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20noble%20souls%20in%20the%20committee%20and%20outside%20were%20%3C%2Fspan%3Einvested%3Cspan%3E%20in%20her%20personal%20life%2C%20and%20they%20possibly%20saw%20in%20this%20complaint%20as%20an%20opportunity%20to%20chastise%20her%20for%20questioning%20absolutely%20everything%20this%20government%20stands%20for.%20Why%2C%20otherwise%2C%20would%20they%20have%20taken%20on%20trust%20and%20admitted%20the%20complaint%20against%20her%20that%20was%20made%20by%20a%20man%20whom%20she%20immediately%20declared%2C%20with%20disarming%20candour%2C%20as%20a%20jilted%20ex%3F%20Can%20it%20be%20because%20the%20intermediary%20was%20Nishikant%20Dubey%2C%20an%20MP%20whose%20bonafides%20are%20beyond%20question%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhy%20would%20they%20have%20then%20called%20upon%20her%20to%20tell%20her%20story%2C%20which%20presumably%20started%20with%20her%20involvement%20with%20lawyer%20Jai%20Anant%20Dehadrai%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fkaali-row-mahua-moitra-says-people-can-imagine-gods-as-they-like-tmc-distances-itself%5C%22%3EMahua%20Moitra%20Says%20People%20Can%20Imagine%20Gods%20as%20They%20Like%2C%20Rattled%20TMC%20Distances%20Itself%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20salacious%20questions%20were%20apparently%20put%20to%20her%20thereafter%20about%20Hiranandani%E2%80%99s%20wife%20by%20Sonkar%2C%20nobody%20from%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20Ethics%20Committee%20intervened.%20It%20was%20left%20to%20opposition%20members%20to%20protest.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20women%20members%E2%80%99%20acquiescence%20in%20this%20interrogation%20is%20yet%20another%20display%20of%20their%20ideological%20moorings%20and%20their%20staunch%20adherence%20to%20these%20regulated%20ideals%20of%20womanhood.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20stand%20in%20implicit%20contrast%20to%20the%20apparent%20chaos%20in%20the%20lives%20of%20unregulated%20women.%20The%20BJP%20members%20of%20this%20committee%2C%20both%20men%20and%20women%2C%20in%20speech%20as%20well%20as%20in%20action%2C%20are%20thus%20representative%20of%20the%20gaze%20it%20trains%20upon%20women%20who%20don%E2%80%99t%20conform%2C%20women%20who%20display%20sexual%20agency%2C%20who%20have%20autonomy%2C%20no%20husbands%20or%20children%2C%20%3Cem%3Esaas%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20%3Cem%3Esasur%20(parents%20in-law)%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20who%20are%2C%20in%20other%20words%2C%20fair%20game.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENishikant%20Dubey%20is%2C%20therefore%2C%20both%20via%20media%20and%20fixer%2C%20the%20hero%20of%20this%20cautionary%20tale.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20was%20called%20and%20%E2%80%98questioned%E2%80%99%20by%20the%20Ethics%20Committee%2C%20hailed-by%20himself%2C%20as%20a%20fearless%20crusader%20for%20the%20nation%2C%20its%20security%20and%20the%20prime%20minister.%20His%20harassment%20of%20other%20MPs%20in%20parliament%20is%20both%20routine%20and%20exemplary%2C%20as%20is%20his%20continual%20breaching%20of%20any%20kind%20of%20sansadya%20(parliamentary)%20honour%20or%20dignity.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInterestingly%20and%20chillingly%20enough%2C%20the%20question%20of%20%E2%80%98sadan%20ki%20garima%E2%80%99%2C%20what%20is%20permissible%20or%20not%2C%20is%20not%20even%20referred%20to%20when%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Ramesh%20Bhiduri%2C%20in%20September%20this%20year%2C%20called%20fellow%20MP%20Danish%20Ali%20a%20pimp%2C%20a%20terrorist%20and%20other%20derogatory%20terms%20used%20for%20the%20Muslim%20community.%20These%20are%20the%20worst%20sorts%20of%20communal%20slurs%2C%20and%20were%20voiced%20within%20the%20precincts%20of%20parliament.%20Ali%20subsequently%20complained%20he%20was%20not%20given%20a%20hearing%2C%20though%20he%20gave%20letters%20to%20the%20speaker%20and%20multiple%20interviews%20to%20TV%20channels.%20No%20action%20has%20been%20taken%20against%20Bidhuri%2C%20in%20contrast%20to%20the%20stunning%20speed%20of%20the%20inquiry%20against%20Moitra.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20the%20time%20one%20of%20the%20few%20MPs%20who%20gave%20an%20interview%20condemning%20Bidhuri%20was%20Moitra.%20She%20expressed%20her%20outrage%20at%20this%20sort%20of%20language%20being%20used%20in%20parliament%20and%20condemned%20the%20absolutely%20despicable%20nature%20of%20this%20assault%20that%20Ali%20himself%20called%20a%20%E2%80%98verbal%20lynching%E2%80%99.%20Ali%2C%20also%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Ethics%20committee%2C%20has%20defended%20Moitra%2C%20and%20has%20been%20given%20a%20rap%20on%20the%20knuckles%20by%20his%20BJP%20peers%20in%20the%20committee%20for%20breaching%20the%20boundaries.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESignificantly%2C%20Dubey%20featured%20in%20the%20Bidhuri-Ali%20incident%20as%20well.%20He%20swore%20that%20it%20was%20Ali%20who%20said%20unspeakable%20things%20about%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%20practically%20forcing%20Bidhuri%20to%20utter%20vile%20communal%20slurs.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20entire%20saga%2C%20then%2C%20suggests%20the%20ineluctable%20truth%20that%20disobedient%20women%20and%20Muslim%20men%20will%20get%20what%20they%20deserve%2C%20both%20within%20and%20outside%20parliament.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIra%20Singh%20taught%20English%20at%20Delhi%20University%E2%80%99s%20Miranda%20House.%20She%20is%20a%20writer%20whose%20most%20recent%20novel%20is%20Pilgrimage%2C%20published%20by%20Speaking%20Tiger%20books.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699861582000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2F14110853%2Ffull-1.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmahua-moitra-and-the-question-of-maryada%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20entire%20saga%20suggests%20that%20'disobedient%20women'%20will%20get%20what%20they%20deserve%2C%20both%20within%20and%20outside%20parliament.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmahua-moitra-and-the-question-of-maryada%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Flights%20cancelled%20and%20thousands%20left%20without%20power%20from%20Storm%20Debi%20-%20and%20more%20thunderstorms%20on%20the%20way%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699860480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F11%2F70x70%2Fskynews-storm-debi-ireland_6359393.jpg%3F20231113182954%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fstorm-debi-could-bring-80mph-winds-as-amber