the%20coastal%20region%20of%20Goa%20with%20Narkasur%20Chaturdashi.%20On%20the%20eve%20of%20Diwali%2C%20hundreds%20of%20community-made%20and%20home-made%20effigies%20of%20Narakasura%20are%20paraded%20on%20the%20streets%20before%20being%20burnt%20in%20a%20symbolic%20slaying%20of%20the%20demon%20king.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20Hindu%20mythology%2C%20Narakasura%20was%20a%20powerful%20king%20who%20had%20gained%20invincibility%20through%20a%20boon.%20However%2C%20his%20arrogance%20and%20misuse%20of%20power%20led%20to%20tyranny.%20In%20response%20to%20the%20pleas%20of%20his%20subjects%2C%20Krishna%20confronted%20Narakasura.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20fierce%20battle%2C%20Krishna%20ultimately%20vanquished%20the%20demon%2C%20liberating%20over%20a%20thousand%20captive%20women%20and%20restoring%20justice%20and%20honour.%20The%20victory%20of%20Krishna%20over%20Narakasura%20is%20celebrated%20during%20Diwali%2C%20symbolising%20the%20triumph%20of%20righteousness.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20each%20passing%20year%2C%20localities%20have%20been%20getting%20more%20and%20more%20competitive.%20In%20villages%20and%20towns%20across%20Goa%2C%20groups%20of%20young%20men%20%E2%80%93%20proudly%20labelled%20%E2%80%98the%20Pirate%20Boys%E2%80%99%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98Sanskaari%20boys%E2%80%99%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98Anjuna%20boyz%E2%80%99%20and%20the%20like%20%E2%80%93%20pull%20in%20funding%2C%20come%20up%20with%20a%20creative%20concept%20and%20get%20moving%20on%20getting%20materials%20together%20for%20the%20all-night%20party.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFrom%20one%20demon%20king%20with%20dreadlocks%2C%20to%20many%20more%20with%20sinewy%20muscular%20thighs%20to%20yet%20more%20with%20snake-like%20lower%20bodies%20%E2%80%93%20the%20interpretations%20are%20many.%20The%20effigies%20are%20decorated%20in%20a%20variety%20of%20ways%2C%20from%20golden%20chains%2C%20to%20whips%20made%20of%20neon%20light%