d%20along%20similar%20lines%20of%20renewable%20energy%20and%20solar%20energy.%20Working%20in%20the%20renewable%20energy%20sector%20for%20several%20years%20is%20what%20became%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20why%20he%20perceived%20the%20idea%20of%20Green%20Tiger%20Mobility%2C%20adding%20to%20the%20long%20list%20of%20existing%20innovations%20like%20%E2%80%98battery%20swap%E2%80%99%20and%20longer%20range%20in%20two-wheeler%20EVs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20I%20realised%20working%20in%20the%20sector%20was%20that%20with%20renewable%20energies%20that%20are%20dependent%20on%20nature%2C%20you%20cannot%20predict%20it%20as%20per%20your%20demand.%20In%20a%20country%20like%20India%2C%20where%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20are%20now%20moving%20towards%20EVs%2C%20there%20will%20soon%20be%20a%20huge%20gap%20in%20demand%20and%20supply%20of%20renewable%20electricity%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20line%20of%20thought%20prompted%20me%20to%20consider%20a%20solution%20similar%20to%20the%20setup%20we%20employ%20in%20our%20homes%2C%20with%20electricity%20as%20the%20primary%20source%20and%20a%20generator%20or%20inverter%20as%20a%20backup.%20Why%20can%E2%80%99t%20we%20have%20an%20electric%20vehicle%20equipped%20with%20a%20petrol%20engine%20as%20a%20standby%20power%20source%20to%20ensure%20complete%20reliability%20for%20the%20consumer%3F%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20how%20the%20idea%20of%20Green%20Tiger%20Mobility%20came%20to%20Ashish.%20%E2%80%9CAnd%20that%E2%80%99s%20where%20we%20built%20the%20hybrid%20as%20a%20retrofit%20solution%20to%20give%20a%20bridge%20to%2025%20crore%20existing%20two-wheeler%20riders%20in%20the%20country%20towards%20a%20greener%20tomorrow%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20in%20early%202020%2C%20Ashish%20decided%20to%20quit%20his%2015%20years%20of%20corporate%20career%20and%20finally%20bring%20his%20childhood%20dream%20to%20a%20living%20reality.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn