0which%20mode%20the%20vehicle%20is%20running%20on.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20also%20indicates%20if%20there%20is%20any%20fault%20in%20the%20system%20or%20if%20there%20is%20a%20heating%20problem%20while%20the%20vehicle%20is%20running%20on%20electric%20mode%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20dual%20powertrain%20mode%20or%20the%20retrofits%20are%20great%20not%20just%20because%20they%20are%20eco-friendly%20but%20it%20also%20reduces%20the%20anxiety%20of%20the%20rider%20over%20its%20range.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COn%20a%20daily%20basis%2C%20a%20typical%20rider%20only%20uses%20their%20scooter%20for%20a%20range%20of%2050%20to%2060%20km.%20It%20is%20only%2C%20let%20us%20say%2C%20once%20a%20month%20that%20they%20might%20need%20to%20use%20it%20for%20another%20100%20or%20200%20km.%20So%20instead%20of%20giving%20the%20consumer%20more%20range%20or%20battery%20swap%2C%20what%20we%20gave%20them%20is%20a%20reliable%20petrol%20engine%20that%20will%20cover%20any%20extra%20distance%20that%20you%20want%20to%20travel%20on%20a%20given%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20method%2C%20he%20adds%2C%20saves%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20that%20would%20otherwise%20be%20spent%20on%20petrol%20daily.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fev-1699539988.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20company%20has%20converted%2050%20vehicles%20so%20far.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fev-1699539988.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fev-1699539988-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fev-1699539988-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2