2C%20reach%20Spastics%20at%209%20am%20for%20his%20schooling.%20After%20that%2C%20I%20would%20take%20him%20to%20Haji%20Ali%20to%20a%20place%20that%20offered%20physiotherapy%20and%20speech%20and%20occupational%20therapy%20under%20one%20roof%20which%20got%20over%20by%204%3A30%20pm.%20I%20would%20reach%20home%20by%206%20pm.%20This%20was%20my%20routine%20six%20days%20a%20week%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Sujata.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESince%20Akshay%20can%E2%80%99t%20walk%2C%20she%20had%20to%20lift%20him.%20Travelling%20in%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20fast%20and%20unforgiving%20local%20trains%20at%20peak%20times%20with%20a%20child%20is%20no%20mean%20feat.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20this%20led%20to%20back%20pain%20and%20other%20health%20problems%20for%20Sujata.%20She%20saw%20at%20the%20therapy%20centre%20that%20she%20was%20not%20alone.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20were%20many%20parents%20from%20underprivileged%20backgrounds%20who%20brought%20their%20children%20to%20therapy.%20Many%20had%20to%20discontinue%20as%20they%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20afford%20it%20and%20the%20travel%20was%20too%20much%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESujata%20realised%20that%20if%20they%20had%20a%20centre%20which%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F296192%2Fshraddha-soparkar-provides-free-therapy-to-children-with-disabilities-madhuram-charitable-trust%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprovided%20therapy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20education%20and%20healthcare%20under%20one%20roof%2C%20it%20would%20solve%20all%20their%20problems.%20But%20there%20was%20nothing%20like%20that%20in%20Badlapur%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20nothing%20by%20a%20long%20shot%20within%20Thane%20district%20itself%2C%20she%20realised.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20then%20decided%20to%20take%20matters%20into%20their%20own%20hands.%20After%20all%2C%20who%20would%20understand%20what%20a%20child%20like%20theirs%20would%20need%20better%20than%20them%3F%20They%20did%20a%20survey%20in%20Badlapur%20in%20the%20early%202000s%20and%20found%20that%20there%20were%20189%20children%20with%20disabilities.%20They%20gathered%20their%20parents%20and%20asked%20their%20problems%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMost%20parents%20found%20it%20difficult%20to%20handle%20their%20children%20at%20home%2C%20as%20most%20homes%20are%20small.%20Our%20children%20need%20an%20open%20space%20to%20walk%20around%20and%20explore.%20So%20I%20took%20my%20savings%2C%20got%20some%20funds%20from%20other%20employees%20at%20my%20bank%20and%20bought%20a%20one-acre%20land%20near%20Badlapur%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ravindra.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20built%20Sangopita%2C%20a%20shelter%20home%20for%20disabled%20children%20on%20this%20land%20in%202003.%20Derived%20from%20the%20Sanskrit%20word%20%3Cem%3ESangopan%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewhich%20means%20upbringing%2C%20the%20home%20offers%20a%20holistic%20upbringing%20for%20their%20beneficiaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20home%20was%20started%20with%20two%20children%20in%202003.%20As%20parents%20saw%20the%20facilities%20and%20care%20offered%20at%20the%20facility%2C%20it%20grew%20and%20has%2062%20children%20and%2034%20staff%20members%20today.%20They%20have%20special%20educators%2C%20occupational%20therapists%2C%20speech%20therapists%2C%20along%20with%20vocational%20training%2C%20physiotherapy%2C%20round%20the%20clock%20care%2C%20a%20mini-hospital%2C%20a%20doctor%2C%20a%20psychiatrist%2C%20a%20nurse%20and%20an%20ambulance.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20access%20to%20vast%20open%20areas%2C%20their%20residents%20participate%20in%20games%2C%20yoga%20and%20other%20activities%20with%20gusto.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSee%2C%20many%20parents%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20resources%20to%20handle%20such%20children%2C%20often%20abandoning%20them.%20We%20are%20providing%20an%20avenue%20for%20such%20children%20to%20really%20flourish%20and%20do%20their%20best.%20Parents%2C%20too%2C%20can%20be%20satisfied%20that%20their%20children%20are%20doing%20well%